description:
Season: 20
Original Air Date: 12/21/2006

Shane and Phoebe exchange gifts under the tree. Phoebe is touched when Shane presents her with a handmade jewelry box. Ridge is concerned where Phoebe could be. As Ann and Pamela fly to Los Angeles, Ann admits she is frustrated with the relationship she has with Stephanie. Pamela tries to convince Ann that it is never too late. Felicia is concerned with Eric’s decision to fly in Ann and Pamela for Christmas. Eric is confident it will be the perfect gift for Stephanie. Stephanie gives Alexandria a scrapbook filled with many wonderful pictures of happy times spent with her mommy. Everyone is filled with the spirit of Christmas. The doorbell rings and Stephanie answers the door only to find her worse nightmare standing before her, her mother, Ann.
